  <div class="col-md-6 col-md-offset-2 col-sm-12">
    <div id="updating">&nbsp;</div>
    <script id="template-upload" type="text/x-tmpl">
    <div class="upload">
      {%=o.name%}
      <div class="progress"><div class="bar" style="width: 0%"></div></div>
    </div>
    </script>
  </div><!--End col -->
  <div class="col-md-4 col-sm-12">
    <%= form_for SiteImage.new do |f| %>
      <%= f.hidden_field :site_page_id, value: @site_page.id %>
      <div class="fileUpload btn btn-meflat icon-right btn-lg btn-block">
        <span>点击这里添加照片</span>
        <%= f.file_field :image, multiple: true, name: "site_image[image]", class: 'file' %>
        <i class="fa fa-arrow-right"></i>
      </div>
    <% end %>
    <div class="alert alert-info fade in">
      <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="alert" aria-hidden="true">×</button>
      <ol>
       <li>文件的大小不能超过2MB,请下载压缩软件自动压缩以后再上传大图。<br/>
         <a href="/piczip.rar" target="_blank">点击这里下载照片压缩机</a>
       </li>
       <li>可以同时选择多张图片同时上传.</li>
      </ol>
    </div>
    <p id="current-select">上传成功后，点击下面的按钮</p>
    <button type="button" class="btn btn-active btn-lg btn-block" data-dismiss="modal" aria-hidden="true">保存并关闭</button>
  </div>
</div>
